data.description: Up to $10,000.00 in closing cost credit. Situated on a 3-acres w/yr round creek, this stunning 3-b/r, 2-ba home offers an unparalleled level of peace & tranquility. (NO WORRIES abt power outages w/the Generac Generator). You'll be greeted by the beautifully crafted rock hearth that creates that rustic & earthy ambiance while cozying up to the wood stove. The gourmet kitchen, features modern quartzite counters, sleek appliances, wine cooler & an abundance of storage space. This well-appointed kitchen is perfect for both everyday cooking & entertaining guests w/ease. You'll love the lrg mstr b/r w/its updated bath that provides a spa-like ambiance, boasting black/White granite, contemporary tub/fixtures/finishes. Add'l Features inc: Bamboo/slate flooring, updated guest ba w/marble shower, L/R Fireplace #2, & privacy. Why ever be inside when you have front deck as a true oasis, evoking a sense of Zen with its calming atmosphere & tranquil waterfall fountain...And...the  thoughtfully designed backyard offers the ultimate outdoor entertaining experience. Equipped w/ outdoor kitchen for you to host memorable family gatherings. Enjoy al fresco dining under the stars or gather around the cozy fire pit or relieve sore muscles in the hot tub.The 3-car garage actually fits 3 cars & storage!
